spec_data.Name: gfal2-plugin-http
spec_data.Description:
Provides the HTTP (http[s]://) and WevDAV (dav[s]://) support for gfal2.
this plugin is able to do third-party copy with WebDAV if the storage
supports it.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 09:53:04 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provides the HTTP/DAV support for gfal2
